愛德華醫生，請到腫瘤科來

888
01:00:34,397 --> 01:00:37,264
Lily: Please, please.
別這樣

889
01:00:37,300 --> 01:00:39,131
(sobbing)

890
01:00:43,873 --> 01:00:47,104
No. No. Doctors don't know everything.
不，醫生并不是萬能的

891
01:00:47,143 --> 01:00:49,111
We can get another opinion, look for other treatment.
我們再找新的設備，新的治療方法

892
01:00:49,145 --> 01:00:51,511
- You hear about... - Look at me.
- 你聽說過的… - 看著我

893
01:00:51,547 --> 01:00:53,071
...miracle cures. - Lily.
- 奇跡痊愈 - 莉莉

894
01:00:53,115 --> 01:00:56,380
Oh God. Please, something.
不，上帝，幫幫我…

895
01:00:56,419 --> 01:01:00,048
Mike: What kind of god would do this to a little girl?
為什么上天忍心 讓這么可愛的孩子得此重病？

896
01:01:00,089 --> 01:01:03,024
(Lily sobbing)

897
01:01:07,897 --> 01:01:10,195
Katie.
凱蒂

898
01:01:10,232 --> 01:01:14,396
Katie: Daddy, I can't see you.
<i>我看不到你</i>

899
01:01:14,437 --> 01:01:17,600
Daddy, I can't find you.
<i>爸爸，我找不到你</i>

900
01:01:17,640 --> 01:01:20,108
Daddy, I'm scared.
<i>爸，我好怕</i>

901
01:01:20,142 --> 01:01:22,667
- Katie. - I'm scared, Daddy.
<i>- 凱蒂 - 爸，我好怕</i>

902
01:01:22,712 --> 01:01:24,771
Help.
<i>救我</i>

903
01:01:24,814 --> 01:01:26,543
Help me.
<i>救我</i>

904
01:01:26,582 --> 01:01:28,447
Daddy, help me.
<i>爸爸，快救我</i>

905
01:02:02,353 --> 01:02:04,053
[無網絡]

906
01:02:05,554 --> 01:02:07,419
Okay, how about the wireless?
我還有無線網絡

907
01:02:07,456 --> 01:02:08,946
Come on.
快啊

908
01:02:16,298 --> 01:02:18,630
Give me a signal. Give me a signal.
信號，找到信號

909
01:02:18,667 --> 01:02:20,999
- (beeps) - Computer: Good evening, Mike.
晚上好，麥克

910
01:02:22,104 --> 01:02:23,571
Oh, yes!
太好了！

911
01:02:24,940 --> 01:02:28,706
- (beeps) - Mike?
麥克？

912
01:02:29,712 --> 01:02:31,373
Mike, is that... is that you?
麥克，是你嗎？

913
01:02:31,414 --> 01:02:33,143
- I can barely see you. - Yes yes.
- 我看不清楚 - 是的，是我

914
01:02:33,182 --> 01:02:36,618
- It's like seeing a ghost. - No no no. Yes, it's me.
- 我是見鬼了嗎？ - 不，是我，是麥克

915
01:02:36,652 --> 01:02:38,483
- It's me. It's Mike. - This is a little bizarre.
- 是我，是麥克 - 好奇怪啊

916
01:02:38,521 --> 01:02:40,648
I mean, I haven't talked to you in a year
我是說，一年沒見到你了

917
01:02:40,689 --> 01:02:42,748
and suddenly you pop up in a box on my computer.
現在卻以這種方式和你通話

918
01:02:42,792 --> 01:02:45,124
I'm sorry, Lily. Listen to me, please, quickly.
對不起，莉莉 請聽我說

919
01:02:45,161 --> 01:02:47,755
Look, I'm at work, okay? So why don't you call me at home tonight?
我現在還在上班 你晚上打電話給我吧

920
01:02:47,797 --> 01:02:51,289
I'm trapped in this room, this place.
不，聽著，我被困在了一間房間里

921
01:02:51,333 --> 01:02:53,528
Mike, you're always trapped in weird places. That's your job.
麥克，你總是在奇怪的地方被困 你的工作就是這樣

922
01:02:53,569 --> 01:02:55,434
- No no, please, Lily. Listen to me. - (phone rings)
不是，求你，聽我說

923
01:02:55,471 --> 01:02:57,302
- Please. - Lily Enslin.
- 求你了 - 莉莉·安斯林

924
01:02:57,339 --> 01:02:59,307
- Hi. Yeah yeah. - Lily!
- 嗨，對，對 - 莉莉！

925
01:02:59,341 --> 01:03:01,400
- I've got those. I'll be right down. - No. Lily!
- 對，在我手上，我馬上就下去 - 不！莉莉

926
01:03:01,444 --> 01:03:03,742
Lily, please! Call the cops.
莉莉，求你了！快報警！

927
01:03:03,779 --> 01:03:06,179
Send them to the Dolphin Hotel.
叫他們來海豚酒店

928
01:03:06,215 --> 01:03:07,944
I'll call you back.
我一會兒給你打過去

929
01:03:10,519 --> 01:03:12,714
- You're in the city? - Yes!
- 你在紐約？ - 對！

930
01:03:12,755 --> 01:03:15,246
- 2254 Lexington. - What are you doing in New York?
- 萊克星頓大街2254號 - 你來這干什么？

931
01:03:15,291 --> 01:03:18,727
I'll tell you later. The Dolphin Hotel, room 1408.
等等再和你解釋 海豚酒店，1408房，求你！

932
01:03:18,761 --> 01:03:20,729
- That's just perfect. - Please.
- 又是這樣 - 求你了

933
01:03:20,763 --> 01:03:22,594
You walk out, you disappear. Leaving me what?
麥克，你就這樣走了，音訊全無

934
01:03:22,631 --> 01:03:24,895
Not divorced. Separated? I don't know, it's not clear.
我算什么呢？離婚？分居？

935
01:03:24,934 --> 01:03:27,664
- Suddenly you need me? - Lily, I'm in a real bad spot here.
- 突然間你又需要我了？ - 莉莉，我現在情況真的很糟

936
01:03:27,703 --> 01:03:30,467
- I'm in danger. You understand? - Okay, Mike. Slow down.
- 非常危險，你明白嗎？ - OK，麥克，慢點

937
01:03:30,506 --> 01:03:31,734
You're not making any sense.
我不知道你到底在說什么

938
01:03:31,774 --> 01:03:34,902
There's something trying to kill me right now.
有人要殺我

939
01:03:38,814 --> 01:03:40,577
No, Lily!
不，莉莉！

940
01:03:40,616 --> 01:03:42,743
No no no!
不！不！

941
01:04:07,009 --> 01:04:08,840
(water pattering)

942
01:04:43,746 --> 01:04:45,509
I've got a knife!
我可有刀子！

943
01:04:50,553 --> 01:04:51,781
(grunting)

944
01:05:01,130 --> 01:05:03,121
(mumbling) That's the way out.
哪條路能出去？哪條？

945
01:05:03,165 --> 01:05:05,224
Or that way. Or that way.

946
01:05:08,237 --> 01:05:09,431
All right, that's the way out.
這條能出去

947
01:05:09,471 --> 01:05:10,938
(baby crying)

948
01:05:10,973 --> 01:05:13,066
Lady, let me in!
女士，讓我進去！

949
01:05:13,108 --> 01:05:16,839
- Help! Help! - Please, sleep.
- 救命！救命！ - 快睡覺吧

950
01:05:16,879 --> 01:05:19,609
- Lady, I'm coming through! - Mike!
- 女士，讓我進來！ - 麥克！

951
01:05:19,648 --> 01:05:22,811
Mike, can you help me? Where'd you go?
能不能幫我一把？你去哪兒了？

952
01:05:22,851 --> 01:05:26,287
Mike: I got to get some cigarettes. You want something?
抽煙去了，幫你什么？

953
01:05:28,023 --> 01:05:30,389
Jesus Christ!
天啊！

954
01:05:32,494 --> 01:05:34,223
Mike: I've got to go. I'll be in California.
我要走了，去加利福尼亞

955
01:05:34,263 --> 01:05:36,197
Mike, you can't do this.
你不能這樣

956
01:05:36,232 --> 01:05:38,462
She needs you. She lost a kid too.
她需要你，她也失去了個孩子

957
01:05:38,500 --> 01:05:40,968
You've got an amazing talent for stating the obvious, Pop.
你這不廢話么，爸

958
01:05:41,003 --> 01:05:42,231
You think I don't know that?
你以為我不知道么？

959
01:05:42,271 --> 01:05:44,262
I'm trying to talk some sense into your head!
我在跟你講道理！

960
01:05:44,306 --> 01:05:47,070
- Don't put your hands on me, old man! - Mike!
- 別用手碰我，老家伙！ - 麥克！

961
01:05:47,109 --> 01:05:50,237
Talk? Why change what appears to be the habit of a lifetime, Pop?
講？干嗎要改變終身的習慣？

962
01:05:50,279 --> 01:05:51,712
You were always great at passing judgment,
你總是喜歡亂作判斷

963
01:05:51,747 --> 01:05:53,647
but the problem is you never gave a shit.
事實是你根本毫不關心

964
01:05:53,682 --> 01:05:56,617
I never gave a shit because you're a bullshit writer!
那是因為你是個扯淡作家！

965
01:06:01,190 --> 01:06:02,521
Shit!
媽的！

966
01:06:10,699 --> 01:06:12,223
Hello!
喂？

967
01:06:17,539 --> 01:06:18,699
Oh.
哦

968
01:06:43,732 --> 01:06:45,097
Kevin O'Malley.
凱文·O·麥里

969
01:06:50,572 --> 01:06:53,234
(screams)

970
01:06:55,878 --> 01:06:57,505
No.
不

971
01:06:57,546 --> 01:06:59,514
No no no no no no.
不，不，不，不，不

972
01:07:00,616 --> 01:07:03,141
I can't help you.
我幫不了你

973
01:07:03,185 --> 01:07:04,618
I can't help you.
我幫不了你

974
01:07:06,121 --> 01:07:08,681
No!
不！

975
01:08:00,309 --> 01:08:02,300
(groans)

976
01:08:04,847 --> 01:08:06,940
It's good to be back.
回來感覺可真好啊

977
01:08:11,754 --> 01:08:13,449
That's enough of that.
我在上面見識夠了

978
01:08:22,431 --> 01:08:24,228
Alcohol.
我要喝酒！

979
01:08:26,268 --> 01:08:28,327
I was just checking to see if the accommodations
我只是過來看看您是否 滿意我們酒店的住宿條件

980
01:08:28,370 --> 01:08:29,962
are exceeding your expectations.

981
01:08:30,005 --> 01:08:32,200
You know goddamn well they are!
你他媽的當然清楚我滿意了！

982
01:08:32,241 --> 01:08:35,108
- What do you want from me? - No no no.
- 你究竟想怎么樣？ - 錯了，錯了

983
01:08:35,144 --> 01:08:37,476
What do you want?
應該是你想怎么樣

984
01:08:37,513 --> 01:08:40,209
What do you want, Mr. Enslin?
你到底想怎么樣，安斯林先生？

985
01:08:40,249 --> 01:08:42,911
- You sought this room. - It was a job. I was doing the job.
- 房間你已經看過了 - 工作，我不過是在做我的工作

986
01:08:42,951 --> 01:08:44,976
- I beg your pardon? - My job! I'm a writer.
- 什么？ - 工作！我是作家啊

987
01:08:45,020 --> 01:08:47,989
Oh, that's right. You don't believe in anything.
哦，對了，你什么都不相信

988
01:08:48,023 --> 01:08:49,718
You like shattering people's hopes.
你喜歡鏟除人們的希望

989
01:08:49,758 --> 01:08:51,055
Oh, that's bullshit!
放屁！

990
01:08:51,093 --> 01:08:52,856
Why do you think people believe in ghosts?
那你說說人們 為什么相信鬼魂存在？

991
01:08:52,895 --> 01:08:55,261
For fun? No.
為了好玩？當然不是

992
01:08:55,297 --> 01:08:58,733
It's the prospect of something after death.
是出于對死后的期望

993
01:08:58,767 --> 01:09:01,998
How many spirits have you broken?
你毀滅了多少靈魂？

994
01:09:02,037 --> 01:09:03,834
Mike's voice: She was in so much pain.
她非常痛苦

995
01:09:03,872 --> 01:09:05,931
Lily: I'm sure she's smiling down on us right now.
我相信她一定在上面向我們微笑

996
01:09:05,974 --> 01:09:08,943
What do you want from me?
你到底想怎么樣？！

997
01:09:08,977 --> 01:09:10,274
Huh?
恩？

998
01:09:10,312 --> 01:09:13,338
What do you want from me?
你想怎么樣？！

999
01:09:13,382 --> 01:09:15,043
You...
你…

1000
01:09:16,051 --> 01:09:17,348
you little...
你個…

1001
01:09:17,386 --> 01:09:20,355
(muttering)

1002
01:09:20,389 --> 01:09:22,949
(yelling) What do you want?
你想怎么樣？！

1003
01:09:22,991 --> 01:09:24,982
What?!
怎么樣？！

1004
01:09:28,030 --> 01:09:31,830
I want my drink!
我要…喝酒！

1005
01:09:43,512 --> 01:09:46,242
You win. You win.
你贏了，你贏了

1006
01:09:53,922 --> 01:09:55,719
- Katie: Mommy? - Lily: Hmm?
- 媽媽 - 恩？

1007
01:09:55,757 --> 01:09:57,987
Katie: Why is the Bible purple?
為什么圣經是紫色的？

1008
01:09:58,026 --> 01:10:00,290
(chuckles) I don't know why it's purple.
我也不知道，是結婚禮物

1009
01:10:00,329 --> 01:10:03,787
It was a wedding present.

1010
01:10:03,832 --> 01:10:06,323
My grandmother brought it all the way from Hungary.
我祖母千辛萬苦從匈牙利帶回來

1011
01:10:06,368 --> 01:10:07,995
Someday it'll be yours.
將來這本圣經就會歸你所有

1012
01:10:11,640 --> 01:10:14,336
Are there people where I'm going?
我要去的地方有很多人嗎？

1013
01:10:18,347 --> 01:10:22,511
Hey, you're not going anywhere, kiddo.
你哪都不會去的，孩子

1014
01:10:22,551 --> 01:10:24,143
You're gonna stay right here with us.
你就和我們一起待在這里

1015
01:10:24,186 --> 01:10:26,211
Daddy...
爸爸，人總是要死的

1016
01:10:26,255 --> 01:10:28,553
everyone dies.

1017
01:10:30,158 --> 01:10:32,490
When they're old.
- 只有當人年老后 - 而且是很老很老

1018
01:10:32,528 --> 01:10:34,120
When they're much older.

1019
01:10:34,162 --> 01:10:36,426
Okay, and then they go to a better place.
之后他們會去到一個更好的地方

1020
01:10:36,465 --> 01:10:39,457
And it's beautiful there.
那里非常美麗

1021
01:10:40,602 --> 01:10:42,433
And all your friends will be there.
你所有的朋友都會在那

1022
01:10:48,243 --> 01:10:49,972
Is God there?
- 上帝也在那兒嗎？ - 是的

1023
01:10:51,013 --> 01:10:52,139
Yes.

1024
01:10:53,782 --> 01:10:55,647
Do you really believe that, Daddy?
你真的相信這些嗎，爸爸？

1025
01:10:57,219 --> 01:10:58,982
Yes.
是的

1026
01:11:01,490 --> 01:11:03,481
Mike: You know what I think! We should have done more!
你知道我怎么想 我們應該多做點什么！

1027
01:11:03,525 --> 01:11:05,186
- We did everything we could! - No, we didn't!
- 能做的我們都做了！ - 沒有！

1028
01:11:05,227 --> 01:11:07,491
- We should have helped her fight... - Oh my God.
- 我們應該幫她抗爭病魔 - 哦，上帝啊

1029
01:11:07,529 --> 01:11:09,759
...instead of filling her head full of these stories
而不是給她灌輸天堂云彩 極樂世界這些沒用的童話！

1030
01:11:09,798 --> 01:11:12,062
about heavens and the clouds and nirvana

1031
01:11:12,100 --> 01:11:13,931
and all that bullshit!

1032
01:11:13,969 --> 01:11:15,493
Those stories, she like them.
她喜歡這些童話

1033
01:11:15,537 --> 01:11:17,368
I'm going to get some cigarettes, okay?
我出去抽煙了

1034
01:11:17,406 --> 01:11:19,169
(phone ringing)

1035
01:11:25,769 --> 01:11:27,369
[接收中…]

1036
01:12:55,103 --> 01:12:58,231
Mike's voice: We ponder the situation.
我們仔細考慮

1037
01:12:58,273 --> 01:13:01,606
I'm trying to accurately describe...
試圖精確描述…

1038
01:13:02,878 --> 01:13:05,506
Orpheus on the Orpheum Circuit
心中的恐懼

1039
01:13:05,547 --> 01:13:07,538
bathed in tango light,
探戈光…

1040
01:13:07,582 --> 01:13:10,847
the kind of light that makes the dead...
那種能令死人走出墳墓…

1041
01:13:12,120 --> 01:13:14,315
get out of their graves and tango.
縱情跳起探戈的光

1042
01:13:14,356 --> 01:13:17,450
Now this is level nine...
這是第9層…

1043
01:13:17,492 --> 01:13:19,653
(shivering)

1044
01:13:19,695 --> 01:13:21,663
The deepest level of hell,
地獄的盡頭

1045
01:13:21,697 --> 01:13:25,463
furthest removed from all light and warmth.
遠離陽光和溫暖

1046
01:13:27,402 --> 01:13:29,336
This is six.
這是6

1047
01:13:29,371 --> 01:13:31,999
It's goddamn five.
媽的是5，我看到地毯的圖案了

1048
01:13:32,040 --> 01:13:34,201
I think I see the pattern.

1049
01:13:34,242 --> 01:13:37,507
Yes, I can see the pattern.

1050
01:13:37,546 --> 01:13:38,945
Lily: Mike.
麥克

1051
01:13:38,980 --> 01:13:42,143
Mike, can you hear me?
麥克，聽到我了嗎？

1052
01:13:42,184 --> 01:13:45,278
- Michael, where the hell are you? - Lily.
- 麥克，你到底在哪里？ - 莉莉

1053
01:13:45,320 --> 01:13:47,117
Michael?
麥克？

1054
01:13:47,155 --> 01:13:49,180
- Mike. - Lily.
- 麥克 - 莉莉

1055
01:13:49,224 --> 01:13:51,988
(sighs) Michael, can you hear me?
麥克，聽到我了嗎？

1056
01:13:52,027 --> 01:13:53,517
Lily.
莉莉

1057
01:13:56,865 --> 01:13:59,698
Oh my God. Thank God. Jesus, I've been trying to get through!
噢，謝天謝地，我一直在找你

1058
01:13:59,735 --> 01:14:01,896
- Did you call the cops? - Yeah yeah, they're at the hotel.
- 你報警了嗎？ - 報了，他們就在酒店

1059
01:14:01,937 --> 01:14:03,962
- Didn't you say the Dolphin? - Yes.
- 你剛才說的是海豚酒店嗎？ - 是的

1060
01:14:04,005 --> 01:14:06,473
- You're sure? - Yes yes, 1408.
- 你確定？ - 是的，1408房

1061
01:14:06,508 --> 01:14:09,534
Mike, they're in 1408.
麥克，警察現在就在1408房

1062
01:14:09,578 --> 01:14:11,409
The room's empty.
房間是空的

1063
01:14:11,446 --> 01:14:12,811
Mike?
麥克？

1064
01:14:14,049 --> 01:14:16,540
Michael, can you hear me?
麥克，聽到我了嗎？

1065
01:14:16,585 --> 01:14:18,109
- (grunts) - Michael?
麥克？

1066
01:14:18,153 --> 01:14:20,178
Michael, where the hell are you?
麥克，你到底在什么地方？

1067
01:14:20,222 --> 01:14:22,918
I'm afraid I can't express myself in this climate.
我現在好冷，沒法和你解釋清楚

1068
01:14:22,958 --> 01:14:24,755
Calm down, okay? We'll figure this out.
冷靜下，會有辦法的

1069
01:14:24,793 --> 01:14:26,852
- Don't panic. - I'm supposed to die here.
- 別慌 - 我要死了

1070
01:14:26,895 --> 01:14:29,329
Michael, stop it! You're not gonna die, okay?
麥克，別這樣，你不會死的

1071
01:14:29,364 --> 01:14:31,298
Don't move. I can be there in 15 minutes.
別走，我15分鐘就能趕到酒店

1072
01:14:34,636 --> 01:14:36,934
Mike? Michael?
麥克，麥克

1073
01:14:36,972 --> 01:14:40,100
15 minutes isn't enough time.
15分鐘，時間不夠

1074
01:14:40,142 --> 01:14:42,542
- It'll be too late. - No, it won't be too late.
- 太晚了 - 不，不會晚的

1075
01:14:42,577 --> 01:14:44,044
- Lily. - Don't...
- 莉莉 - 別…

1076
01:14:44,079 --> 01:14:46,479
Actually, 15 minutes is perfect.
15分鐘正好，太好了

1077
01:14:46,515 --> 01:14:48,642
It's perfect. Just come up. Come now.
來吧，現在就過來

1078
01:14:48,683 --> 01:14:50,014
- Good, yes. - I need you.
- 好的 - 我需要你

1079
01:14:50,051 --> 01:14:52,019
You've always been someone I can count on.
現在我就指望你了，莉莉

1080
01:14:52,053 --> 01:14:55,079
I know we haven't talked a lot since... since Katie died,
我知道凱蒂死后我們很少溝通

1081
01:14:55,123 --> 01:14:57,990
- but I need you, sweetie. - Wait!
- 但是我需要你，親愛的 - 等等！

1082
01:14:58,026 --> 01:15:00,426
I can't explain it here. You just have to come here and talk to me.
現在我不能和你解釋 你快過來，我們好好談談

1083
01:15:00,462 --> 01:15:01,588
I miss you too, but...
我也想你，但…

1084
01:15:01,630 --> 01:15:03,359
When you get here, don't talk to anybody.
你到了之后，不要和任何人說話 直接到1408房來找我

1085
01:15:03,398 --> 01:15:04,797
Just come straight up to the 14th floor.
- 走進來 - 閉嘴！閉嘴！

1086
01:15:04,833 --> 01:15:06,994
- Walk through the door. - Shut up! Shut up!

1087
01:15:07,035 --> 01:15:09,162
- It's life or death, sweetie. - Do not come up to the room!
- 這事關生死，親愛的 - 千萬別過來！

1088
01:15:09,204 --> 01:15:10,899
- Okay. - Don't come up to the room!
- OK - 千萬別過來！

1089
01:15:10,939 --> 01:15:12,634
- I need to talk to you about Katie. - Don't! Shut up!
- 我要和你談談凱蒂 - 閉嘴！不要！

1090
01:15:12,674 --> 01:15:14,733
- Lily, don't listen to him! - Yes, good.
- 莉莉，別聽他的！ - 恩，好

1091
01:15:14,776 --> 01:15:16,573
- It's a trick! Don't come up here! - I'll be right there.
- 那是圈套！千萬別過來！ - 我一會兒就到

1092
01:15:16,611 --> 01:15:18,408
(crackling)

1093
01:15:22,350 --> 01:15:24,682
Lily! Lily!
莉莉！莉莉！

1094
01:15:31,426 --> 01:15:33,485
(groans)

1095
01:15:35,597 --> 01:15:37,792
(screaming)

1096
01:15:47,843 --> 01:15:49,310
(moans)

1097
01:15:54,316 --> 01:15:56,580
(girl screaming)

1098
01:15:56,618 --> 01:15:59,485
Woman: My baby! My baby!
我的孩子，我的孩子

1099
01:16:00,722 --> 01:16:03,520
Man: She's heading for the rocks!
我們正沖向礁石

1100
01:16:03,558 --> 01:16:06,789
I don't want to die!
我不想死！

1101
01:16:06,828 --> 01:16:08,159
(women screaming)

1102
01:16:08,196 --> 01:16:11,461
- (dogs barking) - (horse whinnies)

1103
01:16:23,211 --> 01:16:25,702
Man: Oh God!
天啊！

1104
01:16:25,747 --> 01:16:27,840
Man overboard!
有人落水了！

1105
01:16:28,850 --> 01:16:30,977
(screaming continues)

1106
01:16:33,221 --> 01:16:34,882
Come on!
媽的！

1107
01:16:41,696 --> 01:16:43,891
(gasping)

1108
01:17:41,089 --> 01:17:43,057
(coughs)

1109
01:17:43,091 --> 01:17:45,321
(airplane buzzing)

1110
01:17:49,971 --> 01:17:52,971
[廉價汽車保險：15693331408]

1111
01:17:56,972 --> 01:17:59,236
Are you okay, buddy?
你還好嗎，老兄？

1112
01:17:59,274 --> 01:18:00,935
Hey, are you breathing?
你能呼吸嗎？

1113
01:18:02,744 --> 01:18:04,712
Man: Come on, talk to me.
快，和我說話啊

1114
01:18:04,746 --> 01:18:07,146
You guys, give me a hand here!
你們來幫幫我

1115
01:18:07,182 --> 01:18:09,480
(machine beeping)

1116
01:18:14,723 --> 01:18:17,851
Woman: Dr. Edwards to Oncology, please.
愛德華醫生，請到腫瘤科來

1117
01:18:22,964 --> 01:18:25,455
Hey.
嘿

1118
01:18:25,500 --> 01:18:27,593
How are you feeling?
感覺怎么樣？

1119
01:18:29,270 --> 01:18:31,295
- Am I out? - You're okay. You're okay.
- 我出來了？ - 你沒事，你沒事

1120
01:18:31,339 --> 01:18:32,636
Lie down, lie down, lie down.
躺下，躺下吧 沒事了，你在醫院

1121
01:18:32,674 --> 01:18:34,801
Lie down, lie down, lie down. You're okay.

1122
01:18:34,843 --> 01:18:36,401
You're in the hospital.

1123
01:18:36,444 --> 01:18:38,605
Hospital where? In New York?
醫院？哪里？紐約嗎？

1124
01:18:38,646 --> 01:18:40,079
New York? No no, you're in LA.
紐約？不，在洛杉磯

1125
01:18:40,115 --> 01:18:43,084
You got hit on the head with your board.
你的頭撞到沖浪板上了

1126
01:18:43,118 --> 01:18:44,779
I can't believe you still surf.
難以置信，你現在還在玩沖浪

1127
01:18:46,221 --> 01:18:48,018
You flew here just for me?
你飛過來就是為了看我？

1128
01:18:48,056 --> 01:18:51,048
Yeah. Yeah, I was worried.
是的，我很擔心…

1129
01:18:51,092 --> 01:18:53,287
They called.
他們打電話來通知我 認為我們還是夫妻

1130
01:18:53,328 --> 01:18:55,853
I think I'm still listed as your next of kin.

1131
01:18:55,897 --> 01:18:58,331
Okay, I'm not in New York.
好的，我不在紐約

1132
01:18:58,366 --> 01:19:00,834
- I'm out. - Why do you keep saying that?
- 我出來了 - 為什么你一直這么說？

1133
01:19:03,471 --> 01:19:05,666
I was in New York. I was trapped.
我在紐約時被困住了，差點就死了

1134
01:19:05,707 --> 01:19:08,471
In New York, I was dying

1135
01:19:08,510 --> 01:19:10,842
in this Kafkaesque hotel,
在那個鬧鬼的酒店

1136
01:19:10,879 --> 01:19:13,040
the Dolphin.
海豚酒店

1137
01:19:13,081 --> 01:19:16,107
- What? - The Dolphin Hotel on 45th and Lex.
- 什么？ - 海豚酒店，萊克星頓大街45號

1138
01:19:16,151 --> 01:19:17,709
- I spoke with you there. - 45th and Lex?
- 我和你說過的 - 萊克星頓大街45號？

1139
01:19:17,752 --> 01:19:19,913
- I called you. - I've never heard of it.
- 我和你通過話 - 我從來沒聽說過

1140
01:19:22,557 --> 01:19:26,049
You're gonna be okay. You just need to rest.
你沒事的，好好休息下

1141
01:19:43,511 --> 01:19:46,776
Oh, we have a winner.
哇，被開罰單了

1142
01:19:48,850 --> 01:19:50,681
600 bucks.
600美元

1143
01:20:02,097 --> 01:20:04,691
Unbelievable.
太美了

1144
01:20:04,732 --> 01:20:06,893
I can see why you live here.
現在知道為什么你要住這了

1145
01:20:13,441 --> 01:20:15,841
Why did you leave?
你為什么選擇離開？

1146
01:20:22,383 --> 01:20:24,874
Because every time I looked at you,
因為一看到你，我就想起她

1147
01:20:24,919 --> 01:20:26,887
I saw her face.

1148
01:20:37,799 --> 01:20:39,790
Lily: I think it's pretty clear.
很明顯，夢里那個房間就是 你的潛意識，里面全都是你的回憶

1149
01:20:39,834 --> 01:20:41,699
I think in the dream the room's your subconscious

1150
01:20:41,736 --> 01:20:43,567
and it brought up a lot of stuff.
讓你想起很多事

1151
01:20:43,605 --> 01:20:45,402
That's a good thing for you.
這對你來說是件好事

1152
01:20:45,440 --> 01:20:47,465
But this was... I mean, I was down the rabbit hole.
但這…真的是太可怕了

1153
01:20:47,509 --> 01:20:49,909
I was rattled. I was shook up.
我當時極其不安，恐懼

1154
01:20:49,944 --> 01:20:51,809
And I can't shake it. I think after dinner
都嚇呆了

1155
01:20:51,846 --> 01:20:53,313
you should drive me back to the hospital,
我想晚飯后你該帶我去醫院檢查下 看我的神經系統是不是還正常

1156
01:20:53,348 --> 01:20:56,249
- check me into the psych unit. - (chuckles)

1157
01:20:57,952 --> 01:21:00,045
You look really great.
你看上去真美

1158
01:21:00,088 --> 01:21:02,613
I can't believe I'm sitting here with you.
真不敢相信我們現在在一起

1159
01:21:04,125 --> 01:21:05,649
Tell me about it.
我也是啊

1160
01:21:05,693 --> 01:21:07,888
Is everything all right? Can I get you anything else?
請問還有什么需要的嗎？

1161
01:21:07,929 --> 01:21:11,228
I'll have another glass of wine, please.
再給我來一杯同樣的酒

1162
01:21:11,266 --> 01:21:13,826
The same.

1163
01:21:16,104 --> 01:21:17,594
Mike?
麥克？

1164
01:21:17,639 --> 01:21:19,266
Yeah, I'll have another tequila...
我要一杯龍舌蘭

1165
01:21:19,307 --> 01:21:20,797
Patron, chilled, double.
冰的，雙倍量

1166
01:21:20,842 --> 01:21:22,400
Be right back.
馬上就來

1167
01:21:28,917 --> 01:21:30,976
Katie was there.
凱蒂也在那兒

1168
01:21:32,554 --> 01:21:33,987
Mmm-hm.
恩

1169
01:21:36,324 --> 01:21:37,882
Can you imagine
你能想象嗎？

1170
01:21:37,926 --> 01:21:40,292
what it feels like to have the sensation?
能想象到是什么感覺嗎？

1171
01:21:40,328 --> 01:21:42,353
I mean, the very real sensation
我說的是那種真切的感覺

1172
01:21:42,397 --> 01:21:44,388
that I talked to her, like, two days ago?
就好像我2天前才和她說過話

1173
01:21:44,432 --> 01:21:47,196
I talked to her, saw her, touched her.
和她交談，看著她，觸摸到她

1174
01:21:47,235 --> 01:21:49,601
Yeah.
是啊

1175
01:21:49,637 --> 01:21:52,333
I see her every night when I shut my eyes.
每晚一閉上眼我就能看到她

1176
01:21:54,142 --> 01:21:55,769
Yeah, but it was so vivid.
但那感覺太真切了

1177
01:21:55,810 --> 01:21:58,904
It was so real.
太真實了

1178
01:21:58,947 --> 01:22:00,847
Maybe you should write about it.
也許你應該寫寫這個？

1179
01:22:00,882 --> 01:22:03,476
About Katie? Shit.
寫凱蒂？開什么玩笑

1180
01:22:03,518 --> 01:22:06,351
- You always were tougher than me. - Why not?
- 你一直比我堅強 - 為什么不

1181
01:22:06,387 --> 01:22:09,379
Seriously, it sounds like you're ready to deal with this stuff.
真的，看上去 你已經可以坦然面對這個問題了

1182
01:22:13,661 --> 01:22:16,095
Can you stay?
你能留下來嗎?

1183
01:22:25,506 --> 01:22:27,872
I'm sorry.
對不起

1184
01:22:32,580 --> 01:22:35,140
Okay, we have got 148.
OK，是148號

1185
01:22:35,183 --> 01:22:37,674
148 is gonna be right about...
148號就在…

1186
01:22:37,719 --> 01:22:40,483
Uh-huh.
恩哈

1187
01:22:40,521 --> 01:22:43,581
So if you'd like to sign on the line.
好了，在這里簽個字

1188
01:22:45,593 --> 01:22:47,527
Hey! Hey, man!
嘿！嘿，伙計

1189
01:22:47,562 --> 01:22:49,792
You've been gone a while.
你好久沒來了

1190
01:22:49,831 --> 01:22:52,766
Oh, by the way, dude, I read your book.
哦，對了，你的書我看了

1191
01:22:52,800 --> 01:22:56,702
What is it? "10 Most Haunted Motels," right?
叫什么“10座鬧鬼旅館”對么？

1192
01:22:56,738 --> 01:22:58,638
That's some scary shit.
太他媽恐怖了

1193
01:23:02,243 --> 01:23:04,939
See you around.
再見

1194
01:23:42,717 --> 01:23:44,480
Did I drop a postcard?
我是不是掉過張明信片？

1195
01:23:44,519 --> 01:23:46,009
- What? - Did I?
- 什么？ - 是嗎？

1196
01:23:46,054 --> 01:23:47,578
- Huh? - A postcard.
- 啊？ - 明信片

1197
01:23:47,622 --> 01:23:50,216
No, I think I would have seen it.
沒吧，我沒見過

1198
01:23:52,827 --> 01:23:54,488
But if I find it, I'll put it in your mailbox.
但如果我找到的話，會放你郵箱里的

1199
01:23:54,529 --> 01:23:56,190
Okay?
OK？

1200
01:24:09,391 --> 01:24:11,191
[工廠業主從橋上跳下〕

1201
01:24:14,592 --> 01:24:16,192
[從橋上跳下]

1202
01:24:26,627 --> 01:24:29,755
Mike: My experience in the room was terrifying,
房間里的經歷對麥克來說是恐怖的

1203
01:24:29,797 --> 01:24:33,289
a fragmented loop of unease and despair.
那些記憶令他不安和絕望

1204
01:24:33,334 --> 01:24:35,427
1408 was a horrible dream,
1408房是個可怕的夢魘

1205
01:24:35,470 --> 01:24:40,066
yet somehow I awoke from it renewed.
匪夷所思的，我逃脫了 又重新開始了生活

1206
01:24:40,108 --> 01:24:42,508
Sam: Mikey! You sound happy.
麥克！你聽上去很開心嘛

1207
01:24:42,543 --> 01:24:44,306
- You're scaring me. - I wouldn't go that far,
- 你的故事太恐怖了 - 沒那么夸張

1208
01:24:44,345 --> 01:24:46,836
but I must say that the work is just pouring out of me.
不過這故事是我的心聲

1209
01:24:46,881 --> 01:24:49,247
I think I've actually reinvented myself
我覺得在這個科幻回憶錄中 我重新找到了自我

1210
01:24:49,283 --> 01:24:52,150
in the form of a kind of a fictional memoir...

1211
01:24:52,186 --> 01:24:53,915
"Autobiography of a Nightmare:
惡夢的自傳

1212
01:24:53,955 --> 01:24:56,423
Truman Capote meets H.R. Giger." What do you think?
杜魯門·卡波特遇見《異形》之父 你覺得怎樣？

1213
01:24:56,457 --> 01:24:59,255
I love it! "'Ln Cold Blood' with 'Aliens!"'
太棒了！冷血與異形 （杜魯門·卡波特的小說）

1214
01:24:59,293 --> 01:25:01,625
That's sexy. I wanna put it out to auction,
很不錯啊，我拿去拍了

1215
01:25:01,662 --> 01:25:04,153
start a bidding war. When can I read it?
開個高價戰 我什么時候能讀到？

1216
01:25:04,198 --> 01:25:07,031
Easy, tiger. Any day now. You're gonna get it as soon as I finish.
別急啊，很快了 我完成了就給你

1217
01:25:07,068 --> 01:25:09,263
Okay, Mike. Less talking, more writing.
OK，麥克，少說多寫

1218
01:25:09,303 --> 01:25:11,794
Hey, where's that decaf? I'm dying here.
嘿，咖啡呢？我要死了

1219
01:25:26,795 --> 01:25:28,395
[路易斯山療養院總結報告]

1220
01:25:29,296 --> 01:25:30,796
[B部分 醫療保險 - 轉讓債權]

1221
01:25:38,399 --> 01:25:40,196
Thank you.
謝謝

1222
01:25:53,815 --> 01:25:55,339
Hey, Pop.
嘿，爸爸

1223
01:26:03,257 --> 01:26:06,090
How are you doing, old boy?
最近怎樣，老伙計？

1224
01:26:06,127 --> 01:26:09,563
Can you hear me?
你能聽到我說話嗎？

1225
01:26:09,597 --> 01:26:11,792
I don't think so.
不會吧

1226
01:26:21,342 --> 01:26:23,003
I know I haven't been here in a few months,
我知道我幾個月沒來了

1227
01:26:23,044 --> 01:26:25,808
but I just wanted to...
但我只是想…

1228
01:26:25,847 --> 01:26:28,577
come by and see how you're doing and...
來看看你還好嗎

1229
01:26:30,551 --> 01:26:34,180
tell you I was doing okay.
告訴你我還不錯

1230
01:26:34,222 --> 01:26:37,817
Doing pretty good, actually.
應該說過得很不錯

1231
01:26:39,293 --> 01:26:42,751
I started talking to Lily again.
開始和莉莉有話說了

1232
01:26:42,797 --> 01:26:46,494
And I wrote a new book,
而且我寫了本新書

1233
01:26:46,534 --> 01:26:49,367
which I actually think you would like...
你應該會喜歡的

1234
01:26:51,539 --> 01:26:54,133
believe it or not.
相信我

1235
01:26:54,175 --> 01:26:57,542
(sighs)

1236
01:27:01,449 --> 01:27:03,178
Michael.
麥克

1237
01:27:03,217 --> 01:27:06,380
Dad.
爸

1238
01:27:06,420 --> 01:27:09,821
Michael.
麥克

1239
01:27:09,857 --> 01:27:13,224
Yeah.
恩

1240
01:27:13,261 --> 01:27:16,458
Yeah.
恩

1241
01:27:23,604 --> 01:27:26,038
So...
那…

1242
01:27:29,243 --> 01:27:30,904
(horn blowing)

1243
01:27:30,945 --> 01:27:34,244
Man: Hey, you can't park there! Move it down, will you?
嘿，別停在這里，往后停點

1244
01:27:34,282 --> 01:27:37,683
Hey, I got a package I need to overnight.
嗨，我有個加急包裹

1245
01:27:37,718 --> 01:27:40,881
Is this the right form? I got to get this to New York by tomorrow morning.
